reviews.review_text: Excellent recording This 5-star recording has an ambiance not present in other sources. I have been listening to various copies of this show since 1985, and this is the first time that I have heard it as experienced in the Fox.  Thanks!
Best sound for my taste Great show, maybe second best of tour after 11/1. I also think this is the best sounding source. I would rank the Koucky source second best.
